Apparel.cc


List of data files:
defs.h


To run this software, you will need to be in the a1BaseCose directory, then compile by issuing the command "make", after to run the software you will have to issue "./a1".

When the user enters the system, he will have 5 choices to make as following:
1-add a course to the system database, this option will ivoke a function to add a course to the database. Then by pressing enter, the user will be back in the main screen

2-list courses, this option will ivoke a function to print all existings courses.Then by pressing enter, the user will be back in the main screen

3-Delete course, this is a new option and feature. In this option the user will be asked to enter the name of the course he wants to delete, after he enters the system will check if the course code is in the database, if it is the system will delete that course, if not then the system will stand by and ask the user if he wants to continue and that will take the user to the main menu
  
4-add textbook, this option will first ask the user to input a course code, if the code exists in the databse (from option 1), it will then ask the user to input the text book info.Then by pressing enter, the user will be back in the main screen

5-list course textbooks, in this option on the user is successfully verified and the system will print the added text books (from option 3).Then by pressing enter, the user will be back in the main screen

6-List gifts, in this option the user has the choice to add gifts, with different specifications
7-List eletronics, in this option the user has the choice to add gifts, with different specifications
0- exit the system, if the user wants to get out of program, he can just enter 0, and he will exit the system. 
